Battlefield Earth may refer to:
Battlefield Earth (novel), a science fiction novel by L. Ron Hubbard, founder of the Church of Scientology. Battlefield Earth (soundtrack) (also called Space Jazz), companion music soundtrack to the novel, composed by L. Ron Hubbard. Battlefield Earth (film), a 2000 film adaptation of the novel, starring John Travolta.
